flowchart LR
    S[String original] --> TE[TextEncoder]
    TE --> R1[ReadableStream]
    R1 --> CS[CompressionStream gzip]
    CS --> W1[WritableStream acumulador]
    W1 --> UA[Uint8Array comprimido]
    UA --> R2[ReadableStream]
    R2 --> DS[DecompressionStream gzip]
    DS --> W2[WritableStream acumulador]
    W2 --> TD[TextDecoder]
    TD --> SF[String final restaurada]